      <bioghist id="a2" encodinganalog="545"> 
         <head>Biographical Note</head> 
      	<p>Residents of Rockton, Ill. Albion, George, and Herman, sons of Calvin Stevens, served in the U.S. Army as volunteers during the Civil War.</p> 
      </bioghist> 
      <arrangement id="a4" encodinganalog="351$a"> 
